Class WrappedObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.fcdonders.fieldtrip.bufferclient.WrappedObject
  • public class WrappedObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for wrapping relevant Java objects in a way that is easily convertible to FieldTrip data types.
